oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Tittsworth home
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A man standing by a horse with a child in the saddle in front of Dr. Tittsworth's home in the Shady Grove community of Jefferson County. There are three women standing on the porch of the house.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Houses; Families; Horses; Porches
